whatIsRasselDetails1Exp: A safe and accessible online space where you can anonymously chat with one of our Wellness Supporters.
whatIsRasselDetails2Exp: A team of qualified mental health  supporters who are trained and equipped to provide psychological support helping you overcome challenges through chat. They are also here to provide you with mental health self-help resources tailored to your needs.
whatIsRasselDetails3Exp: This service is suitable for anyone who is looking for an easily accessible, private and comfortable space where they can express themselves, or simply anyone who wants somebody to talk to.
whatIsRasselDetails4Exp: O7 Rassel doesn't require scheduling a session; support is here whenever you need it.
whatIsRasselDetails4Exp1: *and get the first month for free
whatIsRasselDetails4Exp2: and get assigned to one of our Wellness Supporters.
whatIsRasselDetails4Exp3: support via text for one month.

onOnOneSessionsGuestDesc: A 50-min online private session with your therapist.
groupTherapySessionsGuestDesc: A form of psychotherapy where one or more therapists help a group of people through collective online sessions, allowing members of the group to receive support and encouragement from each other.
workshopsSessionsGuestDesc: Both online workshops and webinars offer in-depth learning opportunities in different psycho-educational topics. While workshops are more hands-on sessions, provided to a small number of attendees, webinars are for a larger audience, allowing for a broader engagement.
programsGuestDesc: Programs include diverse offerings specialized in a certain psycho-educational topic delivered by a group of selected therapists. The offerings under the program can be online one-on-one or group therapy sessions, workshops and webinars.
assessmentAndTestingGuestDesc: This service includes specialized evaluation for an individual's mental health and behavioral functioning through standardized tests and methods, to be used in diagnosis and determining treatment options.
couplesTherapyGuestDesc: Couples therapy is a form of psychotherapy that aims at helping partners enhance their relationship, through online sessions that the couple attends together or separately.

whatIsO7Faq1: O7 therapy is a highly secure online platform that is dedicated to providing top-tier mental health services to middle eastern communities all around the globe.
forMoreInformationPleaseCheckThe: For more information, please check the
howCanTherapyImproveMyLifeFaq1: O7 Therapy adopts a holistic model which deals with the person as a whole and not just symptoms or disorders. There are highly qualified teams of psychiatrists and psychologists that integrate different therapeutic modalities and use a variety of tools to help reframe your current issues. Hence allowing you to overcome challenges and cope with stressors in many areas of your life.
howCanTherapyImproveMyLifeFaq2: O7 Therapy is committed to reduce the difficulties of face-to-face therapy given the current circumstances. We use cutting-edge technology to provide you with accessible, top-notch mental health care in the comfort of your home.
whoIsTherapistsFaq1: O7 Therapy has a wide network of therapists with diverse expertise and backgrounds. All Therapists in the network are licensed, trained, qualified and accredited with Masters Degree or Doctorate Degree in their field.
whoIsTherapistsFaq3: to learn more about our therapists.
howAreTherapistsVerifiedFaq1: 1. Therapists provide us their cv for initial review by our medical team
howAreTherapistsVerifiedFaq3: 3. Therapists are asked to send all their certificates to be verified and reviewed by our medical team
howAmIBilledFaq: In the sign up process, you will be asked to add your credit card information. At the moment, you can only pay by credit and debit cards. Paypal, Checks and bank transfers are not accepted.
privacyFaq1: Your privacy and confidentiality is our top priority. O7 Therapy was designed with a specialized infrastructure and advanced technology to protect your data and information.
privacyFaq3: details about our privacy and confidentiality standards
privacyFaq5: 1- You can choose to stay anonymous. We will only ask you to add a nickname to be identified on our system, we will not ask you for your full name or contact information.
privacyFaq7: 2- All data is Encrypted using 256-bit TLS encryption End-to-End Chat Encryption allows for a secured communication where only the intended recipient can read the secured message. Zoom uses both asymmetric and symmetric algorithms to encrypt the session. Session keys are generated with a device-unique hardware ID to avoid data being read from other devices. This ensures that the session can not be eavesdropped on or tampered with.
privacyFaq8: 3- Sessions are not recorded Any video or audio communication with your therapist will not be recorded. Only text messages are saved for your reference if you’d like to get back to them and you always have the option to delete specific or all messages saved.
privacyFaq11: compliant O7 guarantees that all technical, physical, and administrative safeguards and company policies and procedures meet
privacyFaq13: requirements of privacy and confidentiality. To read more about HIPPA please follow this
